              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "childNodes": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": "learning",
                  "id": ""
                }
              ],
              "content": "https://www.crockford.com/javascript/index.html",
              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "childNodes": [],
              "content": " ",
              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "childNodes": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": "JavaScript",
                  "id": ""
                }
              ],
              "content": "https://brendaneich.com/",
              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "childNodes": [],
              "content": " and that has been great but, now it's time to go further and with all the things.",
              "id": ""
            }
          ],
          "content": "",
          "id": ""
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "childNodes": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "childNodes": [],
              "content": "I want to ",
              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "a",
              "childNodes": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": "be like Mel",
                  "id": ""
                }
              ],
              "content": "http://www.catb.org/jargon/html/story-of-mel.html",
              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "childNodes": [],
              "content": ". Building this app and writing about it is how I'm going to do it. Also, it's        proving to be pretty fun.",
              "id": ""
            }
          ],
          "content": "",
          "id": ""
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "childNodes": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "childNodes": [],
              "content": "They say that teaching is the best way to identify gaps in knowledge.  After a short time trying to teach, I agree with that.",
              "id": ""
            }
          ],
          "content": "",
          "id": ""
        },
        {
          "type": "ol",
          "childNodes": [
            {
              "type": "li",
              "childNodes": [
                {
                  "type": "italic",
                  "childNodes": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "childNodes": [],
                      "content": "\"If you can't explain it          simply, you don't          understand it.\"",
                      "id": ""
                    }
                  ],
                  "content": "",
                  "id": ""
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": " -",
                  "id": ""
                },
                {
                  "type": "a",
                  "childNodes": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "childNodes": [],
                      "content": "Richard          Feynman",
                      "id": ""
                    }
                  ],
                  "content": "https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Talk:Richard_Feynman#Teaching_quote",
                  "id": ""
                }
              ],
              "content": "",
              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "li",
              "childNodes": [
                {
                  "type": "italic",
                  "childNodes": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "childNodes": [],
                      "content": "\"Simple things should be simple, complex things should be possible.\"",
                      "id": ""
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": " -",
                  "id": ""
                },
                {
                  "type": "a",
                  "childNodes": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "childNodes": [],
                      "content": "Alan Kay",
                      "id": ""
                    }
                  ],
                  "content": "https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Alan_Kay",
                  "id": ""
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": " (Also, find-in-page: ",
                  "id": ""
                },
                {
                  "type": "siteinfo",
                  "childNodes": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "childNodes": [],
                      "content": "egyptian pyramids",
                      "id": ""
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": " - yep, still relevant)",
                  "id": ""
                }
              ],
              "content": "",
              "id": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "li",
              "childNodes": [
                {
                  "type": "italic",
                  "childNodes": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "childNodes": [],
                      "content": "\"If you find that you're spending almost all your time on theory, start turning some attention to practical things; it will improve your theories. If you find that you're spending almost all your time on practice, start turning some attention to theoretical things; it will improve your practice.\"",
                      "id": ""
                    }
                  ],
                  "content": "",
                  "id": ""
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "childNodes": [],
                  "content": " -",
                  "id": ""
                },
                {
                  "type": "a",
                  "childNodes": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "childNodes": [],
                      "content": "Donald Knuth",
                      "id": ""
